# Volume Control
XF86AudioLowerVolume
 amixer set Master 5%-

XF86AudioRaiseVolume
 amixer set Master 5%+

XF86AudioMute
 amixer set Master toggle

# Restart sxhkd
super +r
 pkill -USR1 -x sxhkd
